thread.title: DUNNIHOO, JARROD

author: DUNNIHOO, JARROD
title: DUNNIHOO, JARROD
text: As always,a great price for a superior coffee. Works great in all my machines. If you love crema, this is your coffee. So smooth, rich and when I make my cappuccino...a sweet caramel note. I just wish for the shipping costs, that you would get a faster speed. For the money, you should be getting flat rate priority. That is always the downside when shopping here.
